ana taku pūrereE tino rarahi haere ana te kōheuheu a taku pūrerePūnaha me te mahingaNgā penapena tauriteKua momotu - ka mahia ētahi hipanga ngāwari hei tiaki pūhiko. Ka kore koe e kite i te pōturi, i te āhua pōturi rānei ina tirotiro koe.​Kei te pūhiko hahaka - ka mahia ētahi atu hipanga hei tiaki pūhiko. Tērā pea ka tino pōturi te haere ina tirotiro koe.​Ka āwhina ki te whakaroa atu i te oranga pūhiko mā te tiaki rauemi rorohiko ina mono ai, pūhiko hahaka ai rānei tō pūrere.Ko te nui o te tiaki kei te āhua tonu o tō pūrere, ngā taupānga, me ngā whanonga tirotiro.​Ina te pūrere:Ngā penapena mōrahiKua momotu, pūhiko hahaka rānei - ka mahia ētahi atu hipanga hei tiaki pūhiko. Tērā pea ka tino pōturi te haere ina tirotiro koe.​Whakamahia ngā tiaki mōrahi ki te kore e taea te tūhono ki te hiko mō tētahi wā roa, ā, me tiaki pūhiko anō.(e manakohia ana)He āwhina ki te whakamōkito i te whakapaunga hiko mā te penapena rauemi rorohiko. Ka rerekē pea ngā painga i runga anō i tō pūrere, ō taupānga, me āu anō ritenga pūtirotiro.He āwhina ki te whakaroa i te oranga pūhiko mā te penapena rauemi rorohiko. Ka rerekē pea ngā painga i runga anō i tō pūrere, ō taupānga, me āu anō ritenga pūtirotiro.Ahakoa kua weto pea te aratau tōtika i Microsoft Edge, tērā pea kei te hohe tonu te aratau whāomo Windows me te mahi ki te tiaki rauemi ki tō pūr